used to having hair, longer hair

00:00:16.550 --> 00:00:19.910
and for about three years or so

00:00:19.910 --> 00:00:25.320
when I started to lose the hair, it felt for me 
it just didn't feel natural what I was used to

00:00:25.850 --> 00:00:29.189
so, yeah, it did have slight affects on my

00:00:29.189 --> 00:00:32.720
personality - I would be quite, erm, careful when I
was going out

00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:35.300
thinking should I wear a hat etc -

00:00:35.560 --> 00:00:37.880
so yeah, that's some of the problems with self appearance.

00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:46.640
Well I chose GetHair for the simple fact that

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:51.360
I would advise anybody, do your research
that's the number one priority

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:54.500
don't look at prices. I know

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:58.890
the financial aspect is very important but
the most important thing is to make sure

00:00:58.890 --> 00:01:00.489
you go with a very good company.

00:01:00.489 --> 00:01:03.820
I've done my research, I've looked around

00:01:03.820 --> 00:01:07.660
I've shopped around and 
after coming to GetHair,

00:01:07.660 --> 00:01:11.020
I just thought it was very, very personal

00:01:11.020 --> 00:01:14.130
They treat you very well.

00:01:14.130 --> 00:01:17.950
They're not pushy at all. They ask you what you would like.

00:01:17.950 --> 00:01:22.360
This is what we do, this is how we do it
and it's completely up to you.

00:01:22.360 --> 00:01:23.940
They're not forcing anything to you.

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:27.740
Not trying to push any deadlines, not
trying to say,  come

00:01:27.740 --> 00:01:30.920
by this date just for you to actually come
with them.

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:34.060
They just provide you with the information

00:01:34.060 --> 00:01:36.280
and left it completely into your hands.

