The first day post-operation, it was
great

00:01:44.340 --> 00:01:47.570
the doctor showed me, erm,

00:01:47.570 --> 00:01:50.710
the mirror which had about, probably
this close to my face.

00:01:50.710 --> 00:01:53.860
Looked really good. 
